Kent Sprouse was convicted of the murder of Ferris Police Officer Marty Steinfeldt, 28, at a gas station outside of Dallas in 2002 .
He shot and killed a customer, Pedro Moreno, 38, before shooting another man in the arm .
A jury decided in 2004 that he should be put to death by lethal injection .
In 2004, a jury decided that he was mentally ill and should be spared the death penalty .
Sprouse, now the fifth inmate to be executed this year in Texas, died 22 minutes after being injected .